lead_paragraph: Spanish driver Carlos Sainz will continue to race for Toro Rosso next season, the Red Bull-owned Formula One team said on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Sainz to Stay With Toro Rosso in 2017
headline.main: Sainz to Stay With Toro Rosso in 2017
